	<div class="group">
					<p>Last week, Lynn shared <a href="http://foodsense.is/blog/lynns-monologue">her story</a> with us. Today, she shares one of her absolute favorite recipes - one that she and her husband, Marc, have found, is pleasing to vegans and non-vegans alike.</p>
